    • add

      public void add(int index, E e)
      This method add an Element into linkedList

      If index == 0 Element will add to the first position(same to addFirst)

      If index == size Element will add to the end (same to addLast)

      If index > 0 invalid input: '&'invalid input: '&' index invalid input: '<' size Element will add into linkedList

      Parameters:
      index - position of Element in linkedList
      e - an Element
      Throws:
      IndexOutOfBoundsException - if index incorrect
